09:54.152 --> 09:56.069
Those crowns are a crock.

09:56.154 --> 09:57.321
You know what I found out?

09:57.388 --> 09:58.322
Not real jewels.

09:58.389 --> 09:59.990
A crown hasn't rested on my head

10:00.057 --> 10:03.811
since I won
Miss Tiara Toddler Allen County.

10:03.878 --> 10:05.028
Are you serious?

10:05.079 --> 10:07.397
Yeah, three years in a row.

10:07.449 --> 10:09.199
I dominated
in Western Wear and Runway,

10:09.250 --> 10:11.919
but my real talent
was baby pull-ups.

10:12.003 --> 10:14.588
31!

10:14.672 --> 10:17.207
32! 33!

10:20.745 --> 10:24.014
I was on my way
to becoming Miss Ohio.

10:24.081 --> 10:25.432
That is, until the shoddy
Zizes thyroid kicked in

10:25.517 --> 10:26.884
as well as a love of chips,

10:26.935 --> 10:28.018
and suddenly I was denied entry

10:28.085 --> 10:29.636
into the pageant circuit.

10:29.721 --> 10:31.889
They said I no longer
looked the part.

10:31.940 --> 10:32.856
My dreams were dashed.

10:35.426 --> 10:38.362
There's our future queen...

10:38.429 --> 10:40.764
a size-two
teenage dream.

10:40.815 --> 10:42.533
You know what?

10:42.600 --> 10:44.151
We're going to change that.

10:44.235 --> 10:45.986
How?

10:46.070 --> 10:47.454
Baby,

10:47.539 --> 10:50.290
you're going to get that crown,
and I'm gonna be your king.

10:56.030 --> 10:57.915
Thanks for doing this.

10:57.966 --> 10:59.449
I'm surprised
more girls haven't asked me.

10:59.501 --> 11:00.801
My nose is awesome.

11:00.885 --> 11:03.119
I can totally count
on your vote,

11:03.171 --> 11:05.873
right?
Yeah. To... totally.

11:12.680 --> 11:16.299
So, what's it like?

11:16.351 --> 11:18.268
Looking like you look?

11:18.319 --> 11:20.204
I pretty much have
a warped sense of the world.

11:20.271 --> 11:22.656
Being a hot 17-year-old,

11:22.740 --> 11:25.275
you can get away with
or do anything you want,

11:25.326 --> 11:26.977
so I kind of always assume

11:27.045 --> 11:29.246
that people are always nice
and accommodating.

11:30.331 --> 11:32.332
Okay. So,

11:32.417 --> 11:34.418
we, uh,
ready to pull the trigger?

11:34.485 --> 11:36.820
No, not... not quite yet.
Um, I was kind of hoping

11:36.871 --> 11:39.289
that I could get an idea
of what I might look like

11:39.357 --> 11:40.424
after the procedure.

11:40.491 --> 11:43.544
Um, this is my friend Quinn.

11:43.628 --> 11:45.161
Nice nose.

11:45.213 --> 11:47.047
