25:56.029 --> 25:58.530
to come back, which is why

25:58.615 --> 26:01.400
Santana and I have
started a new club--

26:01.484 --> 26:03.184
The Bully Whips.

26:03.236 --> 26:05.070
The name was my idea.

26:05.154 --> 26:06.705
We're going to be like
guardian angels.

26:06.789 --> 26:09.491
I have deputized
David and Santana

26:09.542 --> 26:11.994
and the rest of their club
to roam the halls,

26:12.045 --> 26:14.713
identifying bullying
and stopping it in its tracks.

26:14.797 --> 26:16.999
I'm saying
I want the pants, okay?

26:17.050 --> 26:19.501
The ones you have on right now.

26:19.552 --> 26:21.587
Then, what will I wear
for the rest of the day?

26:21.671 --> 26:24.172
That's a YP-- Your problem,
not an MP-- My problem.

26:24.223 --> 26:26.475
Hey, Z, back off.
Say what?

26:26.542 --> 26:27.759
What is this? Berets?

26:27.844 --> 26:29.377
Everyone deserves a safe

26:29.429 --> 26:31.013
school environment.
Don't pick on this kid.

26:31.064 --> 26:33.565
It's not cool,
and we won't allow it anymore.

26:33.650 --> 26:35.934
I'm planning on reaching
out to Kurt personally,

26:36.019 --> 26:37.385
through Principal Figgins,

26:37.437 --> 26:39.905
to try to make amends.

26:39.989 --> 26:41.990
This is a chance
to really change this place.

26:42.058 --> 26:43.825
I hope you can support us.

26:50.021 --> 26:53.023
You know, you talk a great game,
but all I'm hearing is talk,

26:53.107 --> 26:55.008
and talk isn't going
to keep Kurt safe.

26:55.059 --> 26:57.227
But the anti-bullying club
that David started will.

26:57.311 --> 26:58.845
The fact is,

26:58.896 --> 27:00.981
since the club began enforcing
the no-bullying rule,

27:01.032 --> 27:02.365
we haven't had one incident.

27:02.450 --> 27:05.351
Yeah, and if I took
all the water out of the ocean,

27:05.403 --> 27:07.821
it wouldn't be wet anymore.

27:07.872 --> 27:12.208
The bullying stopped because
your top offender stopped.

27:12.293 --> 27:14.160
Mr. Hummel.
Can I call you Burt?

27:14.211 --> 27:15.128
Of course.

27:15.195 --> 27:16.463
You remember how understanding

27:16.530 --> 27:18.531
I was about this
when it all began.

27:18.582 --> 27:19.883
I didn't come
to David's defense.

27:19.967 --> 27:21.351
I believed your son.

27:21.419 --> 27:23.703
That's because the David
I was seeing was not

27:23.754 --> 27:25.522
the young man I knew.

27:25.589 --> 27:27.707
The boy I raised
was a Cub Scout.

27:27.758 --> 27:29.509
He was kind,
he was a good citizen.

27:29.577 --> 27:31.210
I still don't know
what was going through

27:31.262 --> 27:32.712
his mind when all
this bullying stared,

27:32.763 --> 27:35.015
but I can tell you
that the David I'm seeing now

27:35.082 --> 27:36.716
is my son, back again.

27:36.767 --> 27:38.768
This... this is real.

27:38.853 --> 27:41.321
Do you have any idea
how much stress

27:41.388 --> 27:43.773
this has caused my family?

27:43.858 --> 27:46.059
My son having
to leave his friends.

27:46.110 --> 27:47.861
My wife and I spending money

27:47.912 --> 27:50.280
we don't have on private school
'cause of your son.

27:50.364 --> 27:53.666
Burt, were you always
so accepting of homosexuals?

27:53.734 --> 27:55.335
We're the same age.

27:55.402 --> 27:56.953
I remember what we used to say

27:57.038 --> 27:58.371
about the gays
when we were younger.

27:58.439 --> 27:59.672
Now, it's taken us

27:59.740 --> 28:01.458
a long time
to figure out what's right.

28:01.542 --> 28:03.576
Why can't you just allow David
the couple months

28:03.627 --> 28:05.512
that it's taken him
to figure it out?

28:05.579 --> 28:07.797
Because he said
he's going to kill my son!

28:07.882 --> 28:09.049
I never actually
meant that, though.

28:09.100 --> 28:10.183
It's just a figure of speech.

28:10.250 --> 28:12.018
How's he supposed to know what?

28:12.086 --> 28:13.553
Your words still matter, David.

28:13.604 --> 28:14.971
I know.

28:15.056 --> 28:17.357
You have to believe
how awful I feel about them.

28:17.424 --> 28:20.060
Those ones, especially.

28:20.111 --> 28:21.694
That's not me.
Not anymore.

28:22.880 --> 28:24.280
What do you think, Kurt?

28:26.934 --> 28:29.152
I believe he realizes
what he did was wrong.

28:29.220 --> 28:30.987
You're only saying
that because you want

28:31.072 --> 28:32.372
to be back in this
school so bad.

28:34.458 --> 28:36.810
Can Dave and I speak
for a moment alone?

28:38.045 --> 28:40.580
You can wait
right outside in the hall.

28:40.631 --> 28:42.916
Let's go.

28:42.967 --> 28:44.834
Yeah.

28:50.975 --> 28:53.309
What's your angle here?

28:53.394 --> 28:55.595
I'm just trying
to make things right.

28:55.646 --> 28:57.797
David, I know, remember?

28:57.848 --> 28:58.965
And I haven't told anyone.

28:59.016 --> 29:01.468
Why? It would have made
your life

29:01.535 --> 29:02.652
a lot easier.

29:02.736 --> 29:04.687
I don't believe
in denying who you are,

29:04.772 --> 29:07.407
but I don't believe
in outing, either.

29:07.474 --> 29:08.808
But still, you owe me

29:08.859 --> 29:10.810
the truth.

29:10.878 --> 29:12.695
What's going on here?

29:16.650 --> 29:18.701
It was Santana's idea.

29:18.786 --> 29:20.153
She wants to be prom queen,

29:20.204 --> 29:22.122
so she figures,
if we can get you back,

29:22.173 --> 29:23.656
we'll get everyone
to vote for us.

29:23.724 --> 29:27.894
I'm both repulsed and impressed
by her Lady Macbethian ways.

29:27.962 --> 29:31.047
Hmm. A Latina Eve Harrington.

29:31.132 --> 29:32.265
Okay, if you're
going to be gay,

29:32.332 --> 29:34.050
you simply must know
who that is.

29:34.135 --> 29:35.935
Look, I don't know
for sure I am gay, okay?

29:36.003 --> 29:37.821
Stop being such
a broken record.

29:39.840 --> 29:42.442
Okay, I have
several options here.

29:42.509 --> 29:45.311
I could tell everyone
the truth about you...

29:45.362 --> 29:47.346
Dude, I said I'm sorry.
You said you wouldn't do that!

29:47.398 --> 29:49.149
Hold on.

29:49.200 --> 29:52.685
Or I can return here
and marvel with pride

29:52.736 --> 29:54.154
at your new
anti-bullying movement,

29:54.205 --> 29:56.156
which I fully believe in,

29:56.207 --> 29:58.291
and further demand
that you and I start a chapter

29:58.358 --> 30:00.660
of PFLAG here
at William McKinley.

30:00.711 --> 30:03.213
Parents, Family and Friends
of Lesbians and Gays.

30:04.865 --> 30:07.700
You need to be educated, David.

30:07.751 --> 30:11.171
You may not have to come out,
but you need to be educated.

30:11.238 --> 30:14.474
Oh, man, just kill me now.

30:14.541 --> 30:17.043
Just keep an eye
on your brother.

30:17.094 --> 30:18.945
One step ahead of you.

30:39.083 --> 30:41.734
You can't be in here, Noah.

30:41.785 --> 30:43.253
It's cool. I checked through
the peep hole I drilled

30:43.337 --> 30:44.570
