it's official.

31:22.276 --> 31:23.276
What's official?

31:23.327 --> 31:24.777
My transfer!

31:24.828 --> 31:26.829
Kurt Hummel's back at McKinley!

31:31.785 --> 31:33.002
Hi.

31:33.087 --> 31:35.004
Let me breathe!
Let me breathe!

