31:36.456 --> 31:38.091
Not yet.

31:38.142 --> 31:40.293
See, there's a reason
we're meeting here today.

31:40.344 --> 31:42.628
There's some people that wanted
to say good-bye to you, Kurt.

31:45.983 --> 31:47.817
Kurt,

31:47.901 --> 31:49.602
Dalton's going to miss you.

31:49.653 --> 31:51.854
You were a great addition
to the Warblers,

31:51.939 --> 31:55.275
