was G. Gordon Liddy...

39:58.392 --> 40:00.059
and he taught my pop
a valuable lesson.

40:00.144 --> 40:02.111
<i>He said the key to any campaign
is digging up dirt</i>

40:02.179 --> 40:04.097
on your opponent,
so I did a little digging.

40:07.067 --> 40:09.068
Dude, my permanent
record has three volumes.

40:09.153 --> 40:11.554
I don't remember
doing half this stuff.

40:13.557 --> 40:15.341
Jackpot.

40:15.409 --> 40:17.443
You moved to Lima
after eighth grade, right?

40:17.528 --> 40:19.479
I transferred from Fairbrook.
That's not a secret.

40:19.546 --> 40:22.081
Well, you must have had
a pretty lousy attendance record

40:22.166 --> 40:22.949
<i>because I called Fairbrook
Middle School</i>

40:23.033 --> 40:23.916
and they didn't have

40:23.984 --> 40:26.269
a record of anyone named Fabray,

40:26.337 --> 40:27.370
which makes sense,

40:27.421 --> 40:28.588
<i>as you actually lived</i>

40:28.672 --> 40:30.123
<i>in an unincorporated part</i>

40:30.190 --> 40:32.458
of Fairbrook Township,
which would have meant

40:32.543 --> 40:34.010
<i>you would have gone
to Belleville Middle School,</i>

40:34.077 --> 40:35.294
not Fairbrook.

40:35.362 --> 40:37.113
So I took a little field trip.

40:37.181 --> 40:38.781
You didn't.
I did.

40:38.849 --> 40:40.133
And you know what?
They didn't have

40:40.217 --> 40:42.352
a record of anyone
named Quinn Fabray, either.

40:42.419 --> 40:44.387
<i>They did, however, have someone
named Lucy Fabray--</i>

40:44.438 --> 40:46.806
Lucy Q. Fabray,

40:46.874 --> 40:48.391
to be exact,

40:48.442 --> 40:50.026
and she looked like this.

40:50.093 --> 40:52.111
You can kind of see
the resemblance

40:52.196 --> 40:55.314
if you look past the nose job
and subtract, eh, 70 pounds.

40:55.399 --> 40:56.599
Stop, okay?

40:59.670 --> 41:00.970
That's me.

41:02.272 --> 41:04.240
My middle name is Quinn.

41:04.291 --> 41:07.943
I stopped going by Lucy because
kids made up a mean nickname.

41:09.129 --> 41:10.279
Juicy Lucy?

41:10.347 --> 41:13.082
Lucy Caboosey.

41:14.668 --> 41:16.502
I hated the way I looked.

41:18.472 --> 41:21.908
I had zits. I was chubby.

41:21.975 --> 41:24.060
I felt terrible about myself.

41:25.946 --> 41:27.213
I didn't have friends.

41:27.281 --> 41:30.032
Nobody would talk to me.

41:30.100 --> 41:34.303
I was the only kid at school who
had to dissect their own frog

41:34.354 --> 41:35.822
because nobody would
be my lab partner.

41:38.208 --> 41:40.460
And then I joined ballet,

41:40.527 --> 41:43.579
lost a little bit of weight,

41:43.647 --> 41:46.249
found out I was athletic,
joined gymnastics,

41:46.316 --> 41:48.818
then cheerleading.

41:48.869 --> 41:50.536
Went on Proactiv for my acne.

41:50.621 --> 41:53.005
And when my dad got transferred

41:53.073 --> 41:56.809
and got a raise, I asked him
if I could get a nose job.

41:56.877 --> 42:00.863
And he said yes.

42:00.931 --> 42:03.850
Then I asked them
to call me Quinn.

42:05.436 --> 42:06.886
So you hate yourself.

42:06.954 --> 42:08.554
No, I love myself.

42:08.639 --> 42:10.089
And that's why I did
all those things.

42:11.792 --> 42:15.528
I've been that girl,
and I'm never going back.

42:15.612 --> 42:18.397
I was a miserable little girl.

42:18.482 --> 42:20.700
And now I'm going
to be prom queen.

42:20.784 --> 42:23.936
Yeah. See, I wouldn't be
so sure about that.

42:24.004 --> 42:26.155
You think everyone's going
to vote for you

42:26.206 --> 42:28.274
because they want
to be like you.

42:28.342 --> 42:30.993
Well, I don't know if they're
going to want to be like you

42:31.044 --> 42:33.296
when they find out
that you're a complete fraud.

42:33.363 --> 42:35.047
What are you going to do?

42:35.132 --> 42:37.133
If I were you,
I'd check the bulletin boards.

43:02.326 --> 43:04.494
Why did you bring me here?

43:04.561 --> 43:05.895
Is there a sale at Claire's?

43:05.946 --> 43:08.080
I brought you here to
knock some sense into you.

43:08.165 --> 43:10.199
You won't listen to me,
you won't listen to Finn.

43:10.250 --> 43:11.868
But you will listen
to Barbra Streisand.

43:13.370 --> 43:14.587
Thanks, Puck. I'll
take it from here.

43:14.671 --> 43:15.922
Nice effort.

43:16.006 --> 43:17.373
But only I can lead
this Barbravention.

43:17.424 --> 43:19.742
Is she here?
No. This is a mall in Ohio.

43:19.793 --> 43:21.093
Look, Rachel, here's the deal.

43:21.178 --> 43:22.411
Do you want to disappoint her?

43:22.462 --> 43:24.246
Who?
Barbra.

43:24.298 --> 43:26.582
Of course not, Kurt.
She's my idol. Okay, if you get

43:26.633 --> 43:28.134
