could only be defined

43:32.306 --> 43:34.223
by the blonde, chiseled faces
of Hitchcock's beauties,

43:34.274 --> 43:36.475
so she redefined
what beauty was

43:36.560 --> 43:38.361
and became the biggest
female star in the world.

43:38.428 --> 43:39.979
But what if
I can't be like her?

43:40.063 --> 43:41.430
Isn't she one in a billion?

43:41.481 --> 43:43.299
