obsessive-compulsive disorder.

47:06.507 --> 47:08.925
Really?

47:08.976 --> 47:10.843
OCD's very treatable.

47:10.928 --> 47:13.796
A combination of medication
and behavioral therapy

47:13.847 --> 47:16.816
will give you some relief
from those feelings of...

47:16.900 --> 47:18.885
