47:24.691 --> 47:27.827
There's a stigma in this country

47:27.895 --> 47:29.612
about mental illness.

47:29.680 --> 47:34.684
I mean, depression,
anxiety, OCD, bipolar,

47:34.751 --> 47:37.019
they're hard to diagnose, so...

47:37.087 --> 47:39.956
