and said they had diabetes,

48:21.682 --> 48:24.634
would you give them insulin

48:24.701 --> 48:28.588
or would you say, "Hey, that's
just who you're supposed to be."

48:28.672 --> 48:31.591
I...

48:31.658 --> 48:35.144
I just feel, um...

48:35.211 --> 48:37.346
I feel so ashamed.

48:39.316 --> 48:41.117
Right.

48:41.184 --> 48:42.852
Well, you're not alone.

48:44.438 --> 48:47.607
