49:14.351 --> 49:16.185
Can I tell you something, Emma?

49:17.387 --> 49:19.171
You're going to feel better.

49:19.239 --> 49:22.358
I promise.

49:22.425 --> 49:24.527
I'm going to give you an SSRI.

49:24.594 --> 49:27.196
Start with a low dosage,

49:27.263 --> 49:29.482
and that'll help you
hold on to the serotonin

49:29.566 --> 49:31.033
that your brain
naturally makes anyway.

49:31.101 --> 49:33.402
And I'd like to see
you in about a week.

49:40.827 --> 49:41.877
Hey.

49:41.945 --> 49:43.379
