You think so?

50:07.187 --> 50:09.388
Mm-hmm.
'Cause I think it's the first one

50:09.456 --> 50:12.074
where you can really see her.

50:21.001 --> 50:23.252
Thank you.

50:23.319 --> 50:25.504
